      <p style="font-size:.82rem; color:var(--ink-light); margin:0;">If you choose to join SEO Writing AI through this link, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you.</p>
    </div>

    <section id="overview">
      <h2>SEO Writing AI Overview &amp; Pricing</h2>
      <p>SEO Writing AI operates on a freemium SaaS model with four paid tiers plus a free plan. All pricing below was verified from the official pricing page captured on July 4, 2026. Annual billing saves approximately 25% across all tiers.</p>

      <h3>What's Included</h3>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>One-click SEO article generation:</strong> Enter a keyword and receive a complete long-form article optimised for search rankings, with auto-analysed SERP competitor data informing structure and keyword placement.</li>
        <li><strong>Bulk article generation:</strong> Generate up to 100 articles in a single batch from a keyword list. Articles can be auto-scheduled on WordPress with staggered publishing times.</li>
        <li><strong>WordPress MCP integration:</strong> Direct auto-publishing to WordPress with auto-generated meta titles, meta descriptions, and image alt tags. Plugin rating: 4.9/5 from 117 reviews.</li>
        <li><strong>NLP SEO checker:</strong> Built-in content scoring evaluates keyword placement, readability, content depth, and technical SEO elements, providing actionable recommendations to reach 100% optimisation.</li>
        <li><strong>Amazon affiliate article builder:</strong> Enter product URLs and ASINs to generate product descriptions, pros/cons lists, specifications, and reviews — purpose-built for affiliate marketers.</li>
        <li><strong>AI text humanizer:</strong> Post-generation tool that removes AI-detection patterns to make content sound more natural. Unlimited on all paid plans.</li>
        <li><strong>Brand voice customisation:</strong> Train the AI on your writing style. Starter: 1 voice, Professional: 5 voices, Pro Plus 2: up to 25 voices.</li>
        <li><strong>Multilingual content:</strong> Article generation in 48 languages with local SEO optimisation.</li>
        <li><strong>AI image generation:</strong> Contextual images generated during article creation, included on all paid plans.</li>
        <li><strong>Rewriter tool, Super Pages, Real-Time SERP analysis, and Connect to Web for internet-linked generation.</strong></li>
      </ul>

