      <h3>Pricing Analysis</h3>
      <p>At $14&ndash;$230 per month, SEO Writing AI is positioned as a budget-to-mid-range AI writing tool. The Professional plan ($59/month, 250 articles) offers the best value and is the most popular. For comparison: Jasper starts at $49/month for a general AI writer without native SEO optimisation, Writesonic starts at $16/month with broader focus, and Surfer SEO starts at $89/month for optimisation only (no writing). SEO Writing AI undercuts most general AI writers while adding specialised SEO features — the Amazon affiliate article builder alone is a feature not available in most competing tools at any price point.</p>

