    <section id="verdict">
      <h2>Final Assessment</h2>

      <p>SEO Writing AI presents a focused, affordable solution for one specific job: producing SEO-optimised content from keywords. It does not try to be a general AI writing platform, and that narrow focus is its strongest asset. The Amazon affiliate article builder, bulk generation with WordPress auto-publish, and built-in SEO scoring create a workflow that directly serves affiliate marketers and content creators — our core audience.</p>

      <p>The limitations are equally important: content quality varies with AI generation, the "SEO effectiveness" claim can only be verified through real ranking data, bulk generation consistency is unconfirmed, and the company behind the product is small. The platform is a tool for accelerating content production, not a replacement for editorial judgment or human oversight.</p>

